    "Gemma 4" : {

    },
    "Gemma 4 单独做 ASR 效果不如 Qwen3-ASR，建议搭配 Gemma 4 润色使用（LLM 引擎也选 Gemma 4）。音频上限 30 秒。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Gemma 4 ASR alone is less accurate than Qwen3-ASR. Recommended with Gemma 4 polish (set LLM engine to Gemma 4 too). Audio limit: 30 seconds."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Gemma 4 多模态模型，支持音频直接转文字。4B 精度更高，2B 更快更轻量。实验性功能。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Gemma 4 multimodal model with native audio-to-text. 4B is more accurate, 2B is faster and lighter. Experimental."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Gemma 4 润色模式：能听原始音频修正 ASR 错误，效果更好。" : {
